John Nell MITCHELL, Applicant-Appellant,
v.
STATE of Iowa, Respondent-Appellee. No. 17-1800 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

An applicant appeals from the summary dismissal of his application for postconviction relief. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
